Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:07.83,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,因為有女孩要考那裡？
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.03,0:04:10.61,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,え　何だって？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:10.61,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,欸  你說什麼？
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.25,0:04:13.38,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,先生が言ってたのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:13.38,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,老師跟我說了
