Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.96,0:07:13.45,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.36,0:07:19.31,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,あ　けど卒業してからどうすんの？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:19.31,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,啊  你畢業之後打算怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.47,0:07:20.10,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,遠距離？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:20.10,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,異地戀？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.48,0:07:21.44,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:21.44,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.56,0:07:23.41,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,出たよ　謎の自信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:23.41,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,又來了  謎之自信
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.21,0:07:25.58,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,同じ高校行く
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:25.58,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,我們上同一所學校
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.01,0:07:26.45,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.01,0:07:26.45,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.03,0:07:30.32,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,何？　彼氏も茜と同じ学校受けるってこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:30.32,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,什麼？  男朋友和你考同一所學校？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.12,0:07:33.76,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,あ　お母さんたちには内緒にしててね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:33.76,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,啊  要跟媽媽她們保密啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.76,0:07:34.96,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,やめときなって
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:34.96,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,還是放棄吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.98,0:07:37.83,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,一生付き合うわけじゃないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:37.83,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,又不是要交往一輩子
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.83,0:07:39.16,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,別れたらどうすんの？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:39.16,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,要是分手了怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.27,0:07:40.30,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,責任とれんの？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:40.30,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,能接受得了嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.34,0:07:44.55,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,気持ちは分かるけどさあ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.34,0:07:44.55,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,我也明白你的感受
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.85,0:07:47.07,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,別れないもん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.85,0:07:47.07,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,不會分手的
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.00,0:07:49.93,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,茜…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:49.93,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,小茜…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.14,0:07:54.32,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,次にまとめの文章を見てみましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.14,0:07:54.32,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,接下來看看文章的總結
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.14,0:07:57.83,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,現在進行形だと「am waiting」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:57.83,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,現在進行時是「am waiting」
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.39,0:08:01.12,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,過去進行形だと「was waiting」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:08:01.12,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,過去進行時則是「was waiting」
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.70,0:08:06.65,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,ただいま
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.70,0:08:06.65,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.81,0:08:08.74,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,おかえり
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.81,0:08:08.74,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.67,0:08:11.86,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,小太郎　ごはん食べちゃいなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:11.86,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,小太郎  來吃飯吧
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.01,0:08:12.76,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,いらない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:12.76,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.21,0:08:22.90,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,何？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:22.90,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.96,0:08:26.88,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,少しは食べておきなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:26.88,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,多少吃一點吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.56,0:09:09.01,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}交際ってマジで
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:09.01,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}真的在交往嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.47,0:09:12.74,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}あれってマジなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:12.74,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}那是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.50,0:09:20.10,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,すっげえじゃん　コタ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:20.10,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,你好厲害  小太
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.10,0:09:22.14,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,水野さんと同じ学校受けるんだって？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:22.14,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,聽說你要和水野同學考一所高中？
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.12,0:09:24.61,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,噂になってるぞ　お前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:24.61,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,你的事都傳開了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.96,0:09:25.94,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,マジか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:25.94,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,不會嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.74,0:09:28.01,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,嘘　マジで？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:28.01,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,我去  真的假的？
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.01,0:09:28.96,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,すごくない？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.01,0:09:28.96,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,這麼厲害？
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.96,0:09:30.12,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,全然　そんな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:30.12,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,沒有啦  怎麼會
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.12,0:09:31.43,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,ラブラブすぎでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.12,0:09:31.43,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,太恩愛了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.43,0:09:32.65,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,結婚しちゃえ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:32.65,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,你們結婚吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.61,0:09:42.18,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,なんかムカつく
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.61,0:09:42.18,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,感覺有些火大
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.18,0:09:43.25,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,リア充め
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:43.25,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,死現充
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.27,0:09:47.38,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,水野さんって　成績いいだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:47.38,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,水野同學  成績很好吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.23,0:09:49.72,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,そこは愛の力でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:49.72,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,這裡就要靠愛的力量了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.72,0:09:51.34,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,んな甘くねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:51.34,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能那麼簡單
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.34,0:09:52.78,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,ギブ…ギブ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:52.78,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,投降  投降
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.14,0:09:56.36,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,本気なの？　お前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.14,0:09:56.36,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,你是認真的嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.70,0:09:57.52,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,何が
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:57.52,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.52,0:09:58.70,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,光明無理じゃね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.52,0:09:58.70,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,光明沒戲唱的吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.70,0:10:00.32,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,偏差値60オーバーだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:00.32,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,偏差值超過60的哦
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.32,0:10:01.74,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,俺ならともかく
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:01.74,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,我的話還差不多
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.94,0:10:04.64,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,俺はコタちゃんの味方だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:04.64,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,我可是小太的伙伴哦
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.83,0:10:06.67,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,お前さっきから近いから
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:06.67,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,你從剛才開始就靠的太近了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.67,0:10:08.12,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,きめーよ お前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.67,0:10:08.12,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,你好噁心啊
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.10,0:10:50.77,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,模試の結果が来てるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:50.77,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,模擬考試的成績出來了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.90,0:10:53.58,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,はい安曇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:53.58,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,給  安曇
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.83,0:10:55.32,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:55.32,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.67,0:11:03.16,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,光明受けるんだって？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.67,0:11:03.16,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,聽說你要考光明？
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.21,0:11:06.21,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,すごいね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:06.21,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.32,0:11:08.54,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,私は第一志望市立にした
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.32,0:11:08.54,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,我第一志願選了市立
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.74,0:11:24.10,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,あの…　３年１組の…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:24.10,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,那個…  我是三年一班的…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.45,0:11:28.23,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,どうも　すみません　わざわざ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:28.23,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,你好  不好意思  讓您專門跑一趟
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.67,0:11:30.56,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,お世話になっております
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.67,0:11:30.56,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,兒子承蒙您照顧了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.45,0:11:55.55,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,大変だね　受験生は
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:55.55,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,應考生真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.27,0:11:58.14,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,成績　よくないから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:58.14,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,畢竟我成績不好
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.70,0:11:59.96,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,そうなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:11:59.96,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.74,0:12:02.83,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,志望校　ダメかも
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:02.83,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,可能考不上志願校
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.81,0:12:06.25,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,顔色よくないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:06.25,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,你臉色不太好哦
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.56,0:12:07.58,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,無理しすぎ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.56,0:12:07.58,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,勉強過頭了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.31,0:12:09.98,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,家族も心配してるんじゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:09.98,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,家人會擔心的吧？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.36,0:12:11.94,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,親は反対してる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:11.94,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,父母反對我考那裡
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.74,0:12:16.03,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,落ちたほうがいいって　きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:16.03,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,肯定希望我落榜
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.69,0:12:20.56,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,辛い時は休んでもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:20.56,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,難過的時候就休息一下
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.18,0:12:23.92,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,気持ちを整えるのも　大切なことだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.18,0:12:23.92,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,調整好自己的情緒  也是很重要的
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.62,0:12:29.43,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,少し落ち着いたら　親とまた話してみたらいいんじゃないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.62,0:12:29.43,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,等自己冷靜一些了  再跟父母談一談吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.54,0:12:41.23,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,ただいま
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.54,0:12:41.23,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.47,0:12:43.61,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,おかえりなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:43.61,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.76,0:13:21.87,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}可愛い
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.76,0:13:21.87,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}好可愛
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.32,0:13:46.65,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,ごめん　待った？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:46.65,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,對不起  等很久了？
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.83,0:13:47.70,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,ううん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:47.70,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,沒
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.52,0:13:52.14,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,２人きりで会うの　久しぶり
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:52.14,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,我們兩人獨處  真是久違了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.61,0:14:12.34,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,あの…　　　　　　　　　あの…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.61,0:14:12.34,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,那個…　　　　　　那個…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.05,0:14:19.41,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,ごめんね　勉強あるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.05,0:14:19.41,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,抱歉啊  你還在學習
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.41,0:14:20.52,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,こっちこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.41,0:14:20.52,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,我才是
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.52,0:14:27.91,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,あ…　あの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.52,0:14:27.91,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,那…  那個
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.05,0:14:29.92,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,メリクリ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:29.92,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,聖誕快樂
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.72,0:14:34.71,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:34.71,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.18,0:14:36.78,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,俺も
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:36.78,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,我也
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.65,0:14:38.42,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,これ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.65,0:14:38.42,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.50,0:14:41.67,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,あ　開けてもいい？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.50,0:14:41.67,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,啊  可以打開嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.67,0:14:42.43,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:42.43,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.00,0:14:47.76,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,部活に使えるかと思って
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:47.76,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,社團活動時應該用得上
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.18,0:14:50.26,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,可愛い　ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:50.26,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,好可愛  謝謝
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.68,0:14:53.21,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　次俺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:53.21,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,那我也打開囉
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.45,0:14:54.01,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.45,0:14:54.01,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.81,0:14:58.94,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,あ…ああ　あの…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:14:58.94,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,啊啊…  那個…
