Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:03.90,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,抱歉啊  織的不是很好
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.58,0:15:08.41,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,初めて編んだんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.58,0:15:08.41,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,第一次織這個
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.36,0:15:10.14,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,マジで？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:10.14,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.99,0:15:13.58,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,すげえ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:13.58,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,好厲害…
