Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.32,0:18:00.36,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,哇  太好了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.81,0:18:06.32,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,よかったね　茜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:06.32,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,太好了  小茜
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.32,0:18:06.90,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.32,0:18:06.90,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,嗯
