Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:31.40,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,通宵了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.21,0:18:33.05,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:33.05,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,學習
